* Termination Settings
** Auto-termination
***_ Specify inactivity period (minutes)
***_ Cluster terminates when idle
***_ Config remains for restart
** Interactive workloads
***_ 45-min timeout typical
***_ Allows time between queries
** Job compute
***_ Auto-terminates after job completes
***_ Starts automatically for next run
** Spot instances
*** Worker nodes
****_ Cost-effective (use spot)
****_ Spark handles failures
*** Driver node
****_ Always on-demand
****_ Driver failure = cluster failure
** Decommissioning
***_ Migrates data before termination
***_ Reduces task failures
***_ Recommended with spot instances
@endmindmap
